description: ZG Blockchain Token is positioned to provide the overall solution of intelligent asset transaction issuance and build a decentralized transaction ecosystem relying on the ecology of ZG GROUP. ZGT is committed to solving several major problems in the chain of assets: through the rich intelligent contract components, complete the classification and management of assets on the chain; High concurrency support, more convenient asset circulation and surrounding ecological support (transaction insurance and credit investigation).
name: ZG Blockchain Token
